6 after June 30, 2008. Within thirty (30) days after the publication of
7 notice under subsection (a), ten (10) or more taxpayers in the school
8 corporation or corporations who:
9 (1) will be affected by the proposed lease; and
10 (2) are of the opinion that:
11 (A) no necessity exists for the execution of the lease; or
