Page 24, between lines 21 and 22, begin a new paragraph and insert:
"SECTION 23. IC 20-47-2-2.5 IS ADDED TO THE INDIANA
CODE AS A NEW SECTION TO READ AS FOLLOWS
[EFFECTIVE UPON PASSAGE]: Sec. 2.5. As used in this chapter,
"corporation board" refers to the Indianapolis public education
